google-drive-mcp-agent

This project is an independent, agent-agnostic Google Drive MCP server.
It is not an official Google, Gemini CLI, Anthropic, or OpenAI product.

Source inspiration and compatibility reference:
https://github.com/gemini-cli-extensions/workspace

The referenced Google Workspace Extension for Gemini CLI is licensed under
Apache License 2.0. This repository is a new implementation focused on
read-only Google Drive tools for generic MCP clients.
